race.comment: BRUTAL LOVE (4) was denied by the barest of margins when resuming here 13 days ago. Is sure to have come on from that and possesses enough dash to offset the wide alley. Can go one better. OAKFIELD BADGER (1) progressed nicely second up in this grade when beaten less than a length at Tamworth. Open to further improvement third-up and rates a key hope. STAFFA (5) is yet to strike through this campaign but is knocking on the door. Will prove tough to hold out if Layt can utilise the low draw. TURGENEV (6) drops back to a sprinting trip off 42 days and is worth watching for late if they overcook it in front. WESTERN WARRIOR (11) returned with a bang here two weeks ago and will appreciate stepping out to 1200m. Follow up.
